Odaily Planet Daily News StarkWare recently announced the launch of a $4 million venture capital fund to accelerate blockchain innovation in Africa, including: 
-Financial support: Grants of up to $150,000, and more advanced teams can get larger investments (usually up to $500,000); 
-Ultra-efficient infrastructure tailored for all project needs: whether directly on Starknet or as a Starknet application chain/L3; 
-Guidance and technical expertise to help projects succeed.
